# ===============================================================
# M-PESA INTEGRATION SETTINGS
# ===============================================================
# The M-Pesa API requires a publicly accessible URL to send payment notifications (callbacks).
# For local development, you must use a tool like ngrok to create a secure tunnel to your machine.
#
# 1. Start ngrok:
#    In a new terminal in the 'backend' directory, run: ngrok http 5000
#
# 2. Get the URL:
#    ngrok will give you a public HTTPS URL (e.g., https://abcdef123456.ngrok.io).
#
# 3. Set the Callback URL:
#    Copy the ngrok HTTPS URL and paste it below, making sure to append the callback path.
#
#    Example: MPESA_CALLBACK_URL=https://abcdef123456.ngrok.io/api/mpesa/callback
#
MPESA_CALLBACK_URL=https://your-ngrok-url.ngrok.io/api/mpesa/callback
